For Uzz /J ∈ [−0.4, 1] the ground-state is connected to its parent VBS phase of the AKLT model [310], and is a ‘‘symmetry
protected topological phase’’, as also found in Bose–Hubbard [351] or multicomponent fermionic chains [352]. Note

