(4.3)

Non-abelian random-singlet states are also expected for disordered chains of Majorana or Fibonacci anyons [422–424], with

a logarithmic von Neumann entropy whose ‘‘effective central charge’’ pre-factor is given by ln d, where d is the quantum

√

